name: Import.SQL.CfgDateString Prueba Kevin 4
query:
SELECT DISTINCT  
    "TC"."IDStore", 
    "TC"."Fecha", 
    "TC"."Grade", 
    "TC"."DateInsertion", 
    1 AS "IDStatus"
FROM 
    "FemcoDataObjetivesClasificaciones" "TC"
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "DataObjetives" "DO"
    WHERE "DO"."IDStore" = "TC"."IDStore"
      AND "DO"."Date" = "TC"."Fecha"
      AND "TC"."Grade" <> "DO"."Grade"
      AND "DO"."IDStatus" = '1'
    LIMIT 1
)

UNION 

SELECT DISTINCT 
    "TC"."IDStore", 
    "TC"."Fecha", 
    "DO"."Grade", 
    "TC"."DateInsertion", 
    0 AS "IDStatus"
FROM 
    "FemcoDataObjetivesClasificaciones" "TC"
INNER JOIN 
    "DataObjetives" "DO"
    ON "DO"."IDStore" = "TC"."IDStore"
    AND "TC"."Grade" <> "DO"."Grade"
    AND "DO"."Date" = "TC"."Fecha"
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "DataObjetives" "DO"
    WHERE "DO"."IDStore" = "TC"."IDStore"
      AND "DO"."Date" = "TC"."Fecha"
      AND "TC"."Grade" <> "DO"."Grade"
      AND "DO"."IDStatus" = '1'
    LIMIT 1
)

UNION 

SELECT DISTINCT 
    "TC"."IDStore", 
    "TC"."Fecha", 
    "TC"."Grade", 
    "TC"."DateInsertion", 
    1 AS "IDStatus"
FROM 
    "FemcoDataObjetivesClasificaciones" "TC"
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM "DataObjetives" "DO"
    WHERE "DO"."IDStore" = "TC"."IDStore"
      AND "DO"."Date" = "TC"."Fecha"
    LIMIT 1
);
